                  <summary><p>The <title xml:lang="ta">Tēvāram</title>. Contains:
<list rend="numbered">
  <item>The first 6 <title xml:lang="ta">Tirumuṟai</title>s, that is, <title xml:lang="ta">Tēvāram</title> 1-6 (U3).</item>
